  KVM: s390: vsie: Fix delivery of addressing exceptions
  KVM: s390: vsie: Fix possible race when shadowing region 3 tables
  KVM: s390: vsie: Move conditional reschedule
  KVM: s390: vsie: gmap_table_walk() simplifications

